### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Create User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

###

### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}

###

### Update User
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.updated@example.com",
  "name": "John Updated"
}

###

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/{{user_id}}

###

### List Users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users

###

### List Users with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users?limit=5&offset=0

###

### Example with actual UUID (replace with real UUID from create response)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000

###

### Create Multiple Users for Testing
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "name": "Alice Smith"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "name": "Bob Johnson"
}

###

### Test Invalid Email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "name": "Test User"
}

###

### Test Missing Fields
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}